title: P71 Crown Victoria Archive
description:
This is a mirror of 2vmodular's site, p71interceptor.com, it's provided for car enthusiasts everywhere, as a tribute to 2vmodular and the effort he put into providing us with his wealth of knowledge so that we could use it to better our panthers.

I plan to keep this archived copy online for all eternity. This site is to my knowledge essentially un-changed from the way it was when 2vmodular's p71interceptor.com was suspended.


Anyone with any questions (specifically questions related to this mirror of this site) may email webmaster@idmsvcs.com or contact "optik" on the forums at http://www.crownvic.net
